
1  Etii apa te nkata naado olarrabal te rishata enkaji e Saul o enkaji e Daudi; neponari Daudi agolu edoyio enkaji e Saul ashalu.

Ilayiok le Daudi


2  Neikini Daudi ilayiok te Hebron: ore olkikau lenye naa Amnon, le Ahinoam e Yesreel; 
3  ore oliare, Kileab, le Abigail ina oliai apa e Nabal le Karmel; ore oliokuni, Absalom olayioni le Maaka ina tito e Talmai olaiguanani le Geshur; 
4  ore oliong'uan, Adonija olayioni le Hagis; ore oleimiet, Sefatia olayioni le Abital; 
5  ore olayioni le ile, Isrem, le Egla, enkitok e Daudi. Etoikioki kulo Daudi te Hebron.

Eibung'are Abna Daudi


6  Ore etii olarrabal erishata e nkaji e Saul o enkaji e Daudi, neitagolito Abna kewan ti atua enkaji e Saul. 
7  Neeta apa Saul enkapiani naji enkarna Rispa, entito e Aia; nejoki Ishboshet Abna, “Kainyoo pee ishomo iyie ajing'aki enkapiani e papaai lai?” 
8  Negoro oleng Abna te lelo rorei le Ishboshet, nejo, “Kara nanu endukuya o ldia le Yuda? Ore ena olong eton ake aitodolu enkanyit te nkaji e Saul papaai lino, too lalashera lenyena, o too lchoreta lenyena, neton eitu aaishooyo iyie apik nkaik e Daudi; ore taata niking'uanare nanu te nkaraki enkitok. 
9  Metaasa sii Enkai ena te Abna, neitulusoo sii, te neitu nanu aitabaya te Daudi ina apa nainosakinye Olaitoriani ninye olmumai, 
10   aitarasaa enkitoria aitung'uaa enkaji e Saul, neitasheyie olorika le nkitoo le Daudi te shumata Israel o te shumata Yuda, ebaiki Dan o metabaiki Beer-sheba.” 
11  Neitu eitoki Ishboshet aidimu atawaliki Abna likae omoni, amu eturia ninye.


12  Neirriwaa Abna ilkiliku enetii Daudi te Hebron, ejo, “Keneng'ae ena kop? Intobira olning'o lino o nanu, naa ng'ura keaku enkaina ai te nebo iyie pee ayau Israel pooki enitii iyie.” 
13  Nejo ninye, “Sidai; Kaitobir nanu olning'o o iyie; kake nabo toki nanu aayieunye iyie; nchere midol iyie enkomom ai, arashu ake te niyau Mikal, entito e Saul, te nikilotu adol enkomom ai.” 
14   Neirriwaki Daudi ilkiliku Ishboshet olayioni le Saul, ejoki, “Nchooki nanu enkitok ai Mikal, naa ninye apa atisira te nkinyang'a oo suaten iip oo Lfilisti.” 
15  Neirriwaa Ishboshet ilkiliku, neya ninye aitung'uaa olmoruo lenye Paltiel olayioni le Laish. 
16  Kake eshomo olmoruo lenye te nebo ninye, eishir asujaa ninye te nkoitoi pooki o metabai Bahurim. Nejoki Abna ninye, “Shomo, torrinyoyu;” nerrinyo ninye.


17  Neiguanakini Abna te nebo ilpayiani le Israel, ejo, “Ore te nkata naje natulusoyie ning'oruru intae Daudi aaitaa olaiguanani te shumata intae. 
18  Ore naa taata entabai intae; amu eitanapa Olaitoriani Daudi, ejo, ‘Te nkaina o sinka lai Daudi aitajeu nanu iltung'ana laainei Israel aitung'uaa enkaina oo Lfilisti; naitung'uaa enkaina oo lmang'ati lenye pooki.’ ” 
19  Neirorie sii Abna Benchamen; neitoki Abna alo aliki Daudi te Hebron nena pooki naatodua Israel; pooki o enkaji e Benchamen pooki aajo sidain te neas.


20  Ore pee elotu Abna te nebo iltung'ana tikitam enetii Daudi te Hebron, neitobiraki Daudi osirua Abna o lelo tung'ana apa ootii te nebo ninye. 
21  Nejoki Abna Daudi, “Kadumunye nanu alo, naa kaiturrurroki Israel pooki olkitok lai olaiguanani, pee etum ninche aaitobira olning'o o iyie, pee itum iyie aitoreisho te shumata nena pooki naayieu oltau lino.” Neaku eishoo Daudi Abna meshomo; nelo ninye te serian.

Etaaraki Abna metua


22  Ore te ina kata nebau lelo sinkan le Daudi te nebo Yoab eing'uaa enjore, neyau iyarunot kumok te nebo ninche. Kake metii apa Abna te nebo Daudi te Hebron, amu eishoo ninye meshomo, nelo ninye te seriani. 
23  Ore ake pee ebau Yoab o ina jore pooki apa natii te nebo ninye, nejokini Yoab, “Eewuo Abna olayioni le Ner enetii olaiguanani, neishoo ninye meshomo, neshomo ninye te seriani.” 
24  Nelo Yoab enetii olaiguanani nejo, “Kaa iyie itaasa? Ng'ura eewuo Abna enitii, kainyoo pee inchoo ninye meshomo, neaku eshomo? 
25  Iyiolo iyie ajo kiewuo Abna ilo ayioni le Ner alej, neyiolou elototo ino e boo o elotunoto ino e atua, neyiolou nena pooki niasita.”


26  Ore eipang'u Yoab aing'uaa ine aing'uaa ine netii Daudi, neirriwaa ninye ilkiliku metusujai Abna, nerik ninye aashuku teilo kesumet le Sira; kake eitu eyiolou Daudi ina. 
27  Ore ake pee errinyunye Abna Hebron, neya Yoab ninye enkilepata te mpolos e kishomi pee eiro te nebo ninye too nkurrat, ore te ine nerem ninye enkoshoke, neye ninye, te nkaraki ilo sarge le Asahel olalashe lenye. 
28  Ore te siadi, ina kata pee ening Daudi ina, nejo ninye, “Ore nanu o enkitoria ai mikiata entioto ntarasi te dukuya o Laitoriani te nkaraki osarge le Abna ilo ayioni le Ner. 
29  Metaa endukuya e Yoab edoiki o enchumata enkaji pooki e papaai lenye; naa nchoo metaa melai aekata te nkaji e Yoab oltung'ani oata nkimek arashu enkeeya oo lbolot arashu oloibung'i entirma arashu olosesekuani to lalem, arashu ololau endaa.” 
30  Kaae near metua Yoab o Abishai olalashe lenye Abna, enkaraki etara apa ninye metua olalashe lenye Asahel ti atua olarrabal te Gibeon.

Etunukayioki Abna


31  Neitoki Daudi ajoki Yoab o lelo tung'ana pooki apa ootii te nebo ninye, “Entopolos inkilani inyi, nirrotianana ilkuniyiani, ninchirishiri te dukuya Abna.” Nesujaa olaiguanani Daudi ilo sanduku otii osesen. 
32  Nenukaa ninche Abna te Hebron, neyietu olaiguanani aishir te nkurare e Abna; neishir iltung'ana pooki. 
33  Nerany olaiguanani osinkolio lo lkiyioi, ejo

“Keye Abna anaa enaiko olmodai?


34  Meena apa nkaik inono,

nemeena apa nkejek inono;

Ore anaa enabatata oltung'ani

te dukuya lelo torrok itabatate iyie.”

Neitoki iltung'ana pooki aaishiraki ninye. 
35  Nepuonu iltung'ana pooki aailejilej Daudi meinosa endaa eton aa dama; kake einosa Daudi olmumai, ejo, “Meikuna Enkai neijia te nanu, neitulusoo sii, te naishamisham endaa arashu ae toki eton eitu edoyio enkolong?” 
36  Nedol iltung'ana pooki ina, neitiship ina ninche, amu ore apa pooki toki naas olaiguanani neitiship iltung'ana. 
37  Neaku etayioloito iltung'ana pooki o Israel pooki ina olong nchere mme eyieunoto apa o laiguanani pee ear Abna olayioni le Ner. 
38  Nejoki olaiguanani isinkan lenyena, “Aimiyiololo intae aajo olayioni lo laiguanani naa oltung'ani o Turori ena olong te Israel? 
39  Nashal nanu ena olong, hoo naatubukokoki eilata aaput aaitaa olaiguanani; ore kulo tung'ana, ayiok le Seruiya naa kegolong'u oleng te nanu. Nchoo elaaki Olaitoriani olarruoni te risioroto enkarruoisho enye!”

